message: Wrong lexicographical order for 'ai.idylnlp.opennlp.custom.encryption.OpenNLPEncryptionFactory' import. Should be before 'org.apache.commons.lang3.StringUtils'.
Abbreviation in name 'writeEncryptedUTF' must contain no more than '2' consecutive capital letters.
WhitespaceAround: 'if' is not followed by whitespace. Empty blocks may only be represented as {} when not part of a multi-block statement (4.1.3)
